{
  "stem": "5371.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "But in-- in the interim-- I think I mentioned I was a big eater.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And I approached a man in camp which was already months before me there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "It was an older man.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "He was not old, because I was young, so I considered him old.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "He was my oldest brother's age.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And he was a carpenter.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "I knew he worked outside the camp, Auschwitz camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And he had the possibility of acquiring a little more food.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "So I approached him, and I asked him if he could help me with anything in food.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And he said he cannot, but if I know anybody who has gold coins or dollars or German marks, he will be able to help me with a loaf of bread or with a piece of salami.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Well, I immediately went into work and I start asking around.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And I said, whatever I'll get, we'll split.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "Anyway, as-- when we came into camp, everything was taken.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "All the clothes was taken away from us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "But the shoes, they let us take.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "So some people, for some reason, had either gold coins or money in their heels, buried in their heels.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "Well, one of the men, as a young man, he had-- I don't exactly remember, was it marks or dollars.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "But I think it was dollars.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And I really didn't know dollars then.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "But anyway, I took the dollars, and I brought it to him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And the first night, he gave me a loaf of bread, which was a big thing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "So I shared.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "I gave him half, and I took half.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And I took the other half-- my half I shared with another young man from my hometown, which was sleeping above me.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "For some reason, people, because people were hungry, became very envious.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
